quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka simoore Al baqarah."
  44,2,"Allah woondirii Deftere …ìannginnde laawol peewal ngol."
  44,3,"Men jippinirii Alqur'aana, e jemma laylatul qadiri: jemma hebbiniraa…óo barki, Men siforii wonde jertiniroo…ìe ndee Alqur'aanaare."
  44,4,"Ko e nder on jemma, woni ko kala fiyaaku √±e√±aa…óo, humondir…óo e arsike maa lajal ekn, woni ko Allah siinata e nden hitaande."
  44,5,"Me…óen senndira kala fiyaaku √±e√±aa…óo immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde imminoo…ìe Nulaa…ìe."
  44,6,"Me…óen imminira Nulaa…ìe …ìen, yurmeende Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, yurmegol Nulaa…ìe e mun …ìen. Pellet, Kanko Allah, ko O Nanoowo haalaaji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Anndu…óo kuu…óe e annuyeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin. Hunnde e …óin suu…óaaki Mo."
  44,7,"Jey…óo kadi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaa…ìe …óum, haray gom…óinee Nulaa…ìe Am …ìen."
  44,8,"Rewetee…óo e goonga woo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara, wuurnoowo wara alaa, si wana Kanko. Jey…óo on Jeyi baabiraa…ìe mon adinoo…ìe …ìen."
  44,9,"∆Åee sirkoo…ìe yananaaka e …óum. Si ko woni, hi…ìe sikkitii…ói …óum, …ìe woni e fijugol e meere."
  44,10,"Habbitoyo Nulaa…óo, lepte yim…ìe maa …ìadii…óe hewtu…óe, √±alnde kammu ngun ardata e curki fee√±ayngu e gite ma…ì…ìe, hakkee ko …ìe sattina heege muusnge."
  44,11,"Hara curki kin hino sudda yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe wi'anee ontuma: ko lepte muusu…óe woni ko he…ìi on."
  44,12,"∆Åe wona e tororgol Joomi ma…ì…ìe wi'ugol: Joomi amen, huncan men …óee lepte, haray ko men gom…óinoo…ìe ma e Nulaa…óo Maa on, si A huncanii men …óe."
  44,13,"Ko honno …ìe waajitorta, …ìe tuubana Joomi ma…ì…ìe, hara le Nulaa…óo ariino …ìe, …ìannginani …ìe Nulal ngal, …ìe anndi le ko o goongu…óo hoolnii…óo?"
  44,14,"Refti …ìe …óuurnii e goongingol mo ngol, …ìe wi'i mo: ko go…ó…óo goo woni e anndinnde mo, o wonah Nulaa…óo, haa …ìe wi'oyi: ko o haangaa…óo."
  44,15,"Tuma Men huncani on lepte …óen yeru see…óa; pellet, on ruttitoto e keeferaaku e fennugol mon ngol."
  44,16,"Habbito …ìe yo Nulaa…óo, haa √ëalnde Men nanngiroyta yim…ìe maa yeddu…ìe …ìen, wippannde manwde nden Badri, haray pellet, ko Men yottoytoo…ìe e ko …ìe yeddiri kon Allah, …ìe fenni Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  44,17,"Gom…óii Men jerribinoke ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, Nulaa…óo Allah teddu…óo, ari e ma…ì…ìe, himo nodda …ìe e wootin…óingol rewa Allah: on woni Muusaa (yo o his)."
  44,18,"Muusaa maakani Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen: accidee lam e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, tawde ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe Allah. Haqqe alanaa on e maccin…óingol …ìe. Awa min wonannde on, ko mi Nulaa…óo Allah e mon, hoolnii…óo e ko Allah nuli lam yottingol kon, mi …óuytataa mi …ìeydataa e mun."